article.description: Jashawn Talton had 20 points and 11 rebounds as Texas A&M-Corpus Christi beat NAIA-member St. Thomas (TX) 69-59 on Saturday.
article.headline: Talton lifts Texas A&M-CC past St. Thomas (TX) 69-59
article.linkText: Talton lifts Texas A&M-CC past St. Thomas (TX) 69-59
article.story: CORPUS CHRISTI, Texas -- Jashawn Talton had 20 points and 11 rebounds as Texas A&M-Corpus Christi beat NAIA-member St. Thomas (TX) 69-59 on Saturday. Nolan Bertain had 13 points for Texas A&M-Corpus Christi (2-4). Peyton Smith added 11 points. Brian Payton and Nathan Thormaehlen each had 10 points for the Celts. Keaton Shaw had eight rebounds. Texas A&M-Corpus Christi takes on Texas Rio Grande Valley on the road next Saturday. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
